query:
UPDATE markets_extended SET
                    question = $1,
                    description = $2,
                    rules = $3,
                    status = $4,
                    probability = $5,
                    volume = $6,
                    "openInterest" = $7,
                    "endDate" = $8,
                    "resolutionDate" = $9,
                    result = $10,
                    link = $11,
                    "imageUrl" = $12,
                    "updatedAt" = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
                WHERE id = $13
